%% AI Underwriter Agent — Model / decision-logic governance lifecycle (change-management gate)
flowchart LR
    PROP["Propose change<br/>(rule / threshold / model / prompt / embedding)"] --> DEV["Develop<br/>(versioned, documented in model card)"]
    DEV --> VAL["Independent validation<br/>(author != validator)"]

    subgraph Gate["Approval gate (must pass ALL)"]
        E1["Eval harness vs golden set<br/>(no regression)"]
        E2["Fairness / bias test<br/>(no disparate impact / proxy)"]
        E3["Groundedness & safety<br/>(LLM-as-judge)"]
        E4["Sign-off (segregated approver +<br/>model risk / UW committee)"]
    end
    VAL --> Gate
    Gate -- fail --> DEV
    Gate -- pass --> DEPLOY["Deploy<br/>(versioned, audited, rollback ready)"]
    DEPLOY --> MON["Monitor in production<br/>(drift, override rate, predicted vs realized loss, fairness)"]
    MON -- drift / threshold breach --> REVIEW["Scheduled / triggered review"]
    REVIEW --> PROP
    REVIEW --> RETIRE["Retire / roll back"]
